query:
UPDATE questions q
LEFT JOIN boards b ON q.boardId = b.id
LEFT JOIN grades g ON q.gradeId = g.id
LEFT JOIN subjects s ON q.subjectId = s.id
SET 
  q.board = COALESCE(b.code, 'ICSE'),
  q.grade_text = COALESCE(g.level, 7),
  q.subject_text = COALESCE(s.name, 'Unknown');
